ne patch, breast lift and fashion tape, earring support patch, eyeliner stencil, cannula fixation dressing with pad, frame style iv dressing, makeup shields, and makeup tape rolls. Further, it provides surgical disposables, haemostat and medical devices, as well as urology, surgery, orthopedic/physiotherapy, blood banking, and other surgical equipment. Additionally, the company manufacture and undertake job work of coating of various substrates. KMS Medisurgi Limited was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}